data.description: Beautifully redone Ranch  is a great starter home or perfect for the empty nester. This home is a wonderful alternative to apartment or condo living. The home offers an Open Floor Plan with a New Kitchen featuring Quartz countertops, Stainless Steel appliance package with 5 burner gas stove. Laminate flooring.  New Bathroom with marble bath surround and flooring , New French doors out to your fenced yard with screened in Gazebo and paver patio. Newer in the last 3 years is Central Air, tankless hot water heater, newer insulation and sheetrock. Great location, just minutes to the bay, marinas, parks, restaurants and shopping with easy access to Route 9 and GS parkway!
